68頁） 起訴書附表編號1","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/111%2c%e8%a8%b4%e7%b7%9d%2c30%2c20221116%2c2/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,111,訴緝,30,20221116,2","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"訴緝","JNO":"30","JDATE":"20221116","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例等"}